{
  "stem": "1343.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Since it was a small town, we did-- I did not go to a public school, but six of the children of my age, we had a private teacher who was teaching us all along.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at the end of the year, we went to the public school and we passed the examination, and this is how we advanced all the way up through the four elementary schools-- grades until we reached gymnasium, which is the junior high, the beginning of the junior high here.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I enrolled in the gymnasium and went there for four years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At the end of the fourth year, which was in '36.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Yes, I believe it-- excuse me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Let me just go back for one second. '25, '31, and eighth year. '39.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Excuse me, 1939 I stopped gonna school because by that time, one of my brothers, who had a nursery, flowers and plants, I took it over because I used to work with him in the summer.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And from that time on, bad times started.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "First, one of my brothers, and then two of them, and then all three of them we called into forced labor camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I do not know how much time should I--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Spend on this, but I think I skip it because this is where hard times started.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1940, they called my father to the forced labor camp, which at that time, we thought that was a tragedy of immense proportion.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whoever heard of a man of family should be called to a labor camp?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nevertheless, he went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But fortunately, six months later he came back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then the war broke out with Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Germany invaded Russia, and they took my-- two of my brothers to the Russian front.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As forced labor camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
